articles.title: Isaac Go named Gilas Pilipinas' captain for FIBA qualifiers - Rappler
articles.description: Isaac Go takes over the Gilas Pilipinas captaincy as Rey Suerte sits out the third window of the FIBA Asia Cup Qualifiers with an injury
articles.content: Suerte, the previous captain, will not see action after sustaining an ankle sprain just a week before the last leg of qualifiers kicks off in Clark, Pampanga, on Wednesday, June 16.
